# Introduction

This API is a service that provides access to data relevant to the tuition repayment and other financial benefits provided by Tuition.io.
The Tuition.io API conforms to the [JSONAPI 1.0 specification](https://www.jsonapi.org). Please refer to the specification for additional details.
